          <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-chevron-down"></i>
          <p>Why Travlog?</p>
          <p>Partner with us</p>
          <p>FAQ's</p>
          <p>Blog</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lists">
          <h5>Meet Us</h5>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-chevron-down"></i>
          <p>+91........</p>
          <p>info@travlog.com</p>
          <p>205. R Street, New York <br />BD23200</p>
